{
  "stem": "5551.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Amongst the Gestapo in Gorlice, there was a man by the name of Kuszka.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "He was actually a chauffeur for the Gestapo, but, himself, an SS man a Gestapo officer.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And they had sort of a liaison relationship.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Now, the chief of Gestapo was a man by the name of Otto Friedrich.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Otto Friedrich, by a strange coincidence, looked very much like Janusz Keller.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "He was also tall, handsome, wavy blond hair, and blue eyes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Before the action to liquidate the ghetto of Gorlice, my uncle, Janusz Keller, he knew what's coming.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "He gave us money.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And he told us, it is best if you escape the ghetto, at night, into the nearby forest.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And so we did.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Remember that anything that violated the German law was under death penalty.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Of course, staying in the ghetto meant also death.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "[SIGHS] Anyway, we-- it was summertime.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "We escaped into the nearby forest.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And we had money on us, that he gave us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "When I say we, I mean my father, my mother, my brother, and myself.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "We were all quite young people and vigorous people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "In the forest, there was a Polish man, a forester, who had a son.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And the son was a nice, young Polish man of above average intelligence.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "He soon discovered us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And he said, I cannot permit you entry into my house or anywhere near my family.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "But as long as you remain here, I will provide you with food and with information.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And so he did.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "We tried to pay him off.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "He did not ask for money or accept any.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And he was totally truthful and, at least for the brief period that we were in that forest, he was-- he was a life saver.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
